<s docid="AP890112-0071" num="15" wdcount="12"> The BBC will show ``Hirohito 
_ Behind the Myth'' on Jan. 24.</s>

<s docid="AP890112-0071" num="13" wdcount="49"> The documentary challenges 
Hirohito's image as a peaceful man forced to go along with his 
generals' plans and alleges among other things that he: _Must have 
